trans-unit.source: Represents named images, which are stored in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImagesCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerer navnet bilder som er lagret i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImagesCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The NamedImage class represents an image that has a unique name, and is useful when an image is dynamically created using a particular drawing routine, and then specified as the image for one of the image properties of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control.
trans-unit.target: Klassen NamedImage representerer et bilde som har et unikt navn er nyttig når et bilde opprettes dynamisk med en bestemt tegning rutine og angitt som bildet for en av bildeegenskapene for av den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage.Name%2A> property determines the unique name of a NamedImage object.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage.Name%2A>egenskapen bestemmer det unike navnet på et NamedImage-objekt.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage.Image%2A> property determines its associated image, which can be any object derived from the .NET Framework <xref:System.Drawing.Image> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage.Image%2A>Egenskapen angir de tilknyttede bildet, som kan være et objekt som er avledet fra .NET Framework- <xref:System.Drawing.Image>klasse.</xref:System.Drawing.Image> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage.Image%2A>

trans-unit.source: When one of the image properties of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control is set by specifying a `string` value, the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A> collection property is first checked to determine whether an image with the specified name exists.
trans-unit.target: Når en av bildeegenskapene for av den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>kontrollen er angitt ved å angi en `string` verdi, i <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A>egenskapen samlingen kontrolleres først for å fastslå om det finnes et bilde med det angitte navnet.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>

trans-unit.source: If a matching NamedImage object is found, this image is used.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det finnes et samsvarende NamedImage-objekt, brukes dette bildet.

trans-unit.source: If a matching NamedImage object is not located, the `string` value is treated as a URL, image resource name, or an image path.
trans-unit.target: Hvis et samsvarende NamedImage-objekt ikke er finnes i `string` verdi behandles som en URL-adresse, ressurs Bildenavn eller en bildebane.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage"></xref> class with the specified name of the named image and its associated image.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage"> </xref> type med det angitte navnet navngitt bilde, og det tilknyttede bildet.

trans-unit.source: The name of the named image.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på det navngitte bildet.

trans-unit.source: Use this name when setting a named image to one of the image properties.
trans-unit.target: Bruk dette navnet ved angivelse av navngitt bilde til en av bildeegenskapene for.

trans-unit.source: The associated image.
trans-unit.target: Tilknyttede bildet.

trans-unit.source: Releases unmanaged and, optionally, managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Versjoner uforvaltet, og eventuelt administreres ressurser.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both unmanaged and managed resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>å frigjøre både uforvaltede og behandlede ressurser. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> frigi bare uforvaltede ressurser.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the image of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir bildet av en <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The Image property determines which image is stored in a <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage> object.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Image bestemmer hvilken bildet er lagret i en <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>

trans-unit.source: Use <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage> objects for dynamically created images, which can then be assigned to a chart image property.
trans-unit.target: Bruk <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>objekter for dynamisk opprettet bilder, som deretter kan tilordnes til et bilde egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>

trans-unit.source: The image component of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Bilde-komponenten for en <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: This can be any object derived from the .NET Framework <xref href="System.Drawing.Image"></xref> class, for example, a <xref href="System.Drawing.Bitmap"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Dette kan være et objekt som er avledet fra .NET Framework <xref href="System.Drawing.Image"> </xref> class, for eksempel en <xref href="System.Drawing.Bitmap"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the unique name of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir det unike navnet på en <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The property identifies a <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage> object that is stored in the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImagesCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen angir et <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>objekt som er lagret i <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImagesCollection>.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImagesCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>

trans-unit.source: This name must be unique, or an exception will be thrown when the object is added to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Dette navnet må være unike og vil bli utløst et unntak under objektet er lagt til i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Use <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage> objects for dynamically created images, which can then be assigned to a chart image property.
trans-unit.target: Bruk <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>objekter for dynamisk opprettet bilder, som deretter kan tilordnes til et bilde egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>

trans-unit.source: This Name property value is used when you set a chart image property to a <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage> object.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapsverdien dette navnet brukes når du angir et diagram image-egenskapen til en <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>

trans-unit.source: When one of the image properties of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control is set by specifying a `string` value, the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A> collection property—of type <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImagesCollection>—is first checked to determine whether an image with the specified name exists.
trans-unit.target: Når en av bildeegenskapene for av den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>kontrollen er angitt ved å angi en `string` verdi, i <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A>egenskapen samlingen – av typen <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImagesCollection>– kontrolleres først for å finne ut om det finnes et bilde med det angitte navnet.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImagesCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>

trans-unit.source: If a matching <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage> object is found, this image is used.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en tilsvarende <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>objektet finnes, brukes dette bildet.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>

trans-unit.source: If a matching <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage> object is not located, the `string` value is treated as a URL, an image resource name, or an image path.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en tilsvarende <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>objektet finnes ikke, den `string` verdi behandles som en URL-adresse, ressursnavn et bilde eller en bildet.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""></xref> value that represents the unique name of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage"></xref> object stored in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImagesCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""> </xref> verdi som representerer det unike navnet på en <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage"> </xref> objekt som er lagret i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImagesCollection"> </xref>.
